  { "id": "food-01", "category": "food", "hanzi": "吃饭", "pinyin": "chī fàn", "english": "to eat (a meal)", "note": "Literally 'eat rice' — but it means any meal. 吃了吗? 'have you eaten?' is a common greeting." },
